{"title":"伐木者","authors":["顾工"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":3,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"伐木者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顾工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伐木者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你理解吗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伐木者的心灵？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在他屋里坐一坐吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看墙上的图景——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社的新居；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新城的缩影；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白浪中的桅杆；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚手架边的轻云……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一张张图景，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"描绘出伐木者的心灵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他心里不只是一片绿叶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是整个祖国的温馨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊馨［xīn］"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锯声和斧声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锯声和斧声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山山呼应；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺着溪流漂出木筏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像飘出一封封祝福的信。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这信是寄给矿工的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"木柱将排队走进矿井；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这信是寄给社员的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农具将络绎到田野耕耘；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这信是寄给居民的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桌椅将跳进你的客厅；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这信是寄给旅客的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枕木将把你引向仙境……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锯声和斧声山山呼应；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远处，更远处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起重机响起隆隆共鸣……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树林啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要再隐居，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去轰轰烈烈的工地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舒展粗壮的手臂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树林啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要再沉寂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去挤到烟囱和烟囱中间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昂起高大的身躯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树林啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要再窃语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去沸沸腾腾的新城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拥抱千千万万的男女！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}